msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ./modules/salt/pages/formulas-custom.adoc:455
msgid ""
"Allows you to show a field or group if a condition is met.  You must use the "
"https://github.com/TomFrost/jexl[jexl] expression language to write the "
